            <ol>
                <!-- Modul 1: Navigasi Maritim -->
                <li>
                    <strong>🧭 Navigasi Maritim</strong>
                    Dasar-dasar navigasi, pembacaan peta laut, sistem kompas (magnetic & gyro), teknik plotting posisi, navigasi astronomi, dan pengoperasian sistem navigasi modern (GPS, ECDIS, Radar, AIS).<br>
                    <em>Mencakup: Bridge Resource Management (BRM), COLREG, Meteorologi Laut, Oceanografi Operasional, dan Watchkeeping Procedures</em>
                </li>
                
                <!-- Modul 2: Teknika Kapal -->
                <li>
                    <strong>⚙️ Kelas Teknika - Permesinan Kapal</strong>
                    Mesin induk (diesel & steam turbine), mesin bantu, sistem bahan bakar, sistem pelumasan, sistem pendingin, boiler & steam system, sistem propulsi, pompa & kompresor, sistem hidrolik & pneumatik.<br>
                    <em>Mencakup: Engine Room Management, Safety Protocols, Maintenance & Overhaul Procedures, Emergency Response</em>
                </li>

                <!-- Modul 3: ETO -->
                <li>
                    <strong>⚡ Kelas ETO - Electrical, Electronic & PLC</strong>
                    Sistem kelistrikan kapal (AC/DC, generator, switchboard, motor), elektronika navigasi (radar, gyro, GPS, echo sounder), PLC & automation systems, safety & control devices, GMDSS communication systems.<br>
                    <em>Mencakup: Power Management, Automation Control, Emergency Systems, Troubleshooting Procedures</em>
                </li>

                <!-- Modul 4: Bisnis Maritim -->
                <li>
                    <strong>💼 Maritime Business Development (BIZDEV)</strong>
                    Ship ownership & investment, IPO (Initial Public Offering) untuk perusahaan pelayaran, IOP (Integrated Operation Port), crewing agency operations, ship management, PBM (Pelayanan Bongkar Muat), keagenan kapal.<br>
                    <em>Mencakup: Ship Investment Analysis, Chartering & Freight, Maritime Finance, Business Economics, Fleet Management</em>
                </li>

                <!-- Modul 5: Hukum & Regulasi -->
                <li>
                    <strong>⚖️ Hukum & Regulasi Maritim Internasional</strong>
                    UN Convention on the Law of the Sea (UNCLOS), IMO Conventions (SOLAS, MARPOL, STCW, MLC, ISM Code, ISPS Code), IACS Member Regulations, P&I Insurance, maritime lien & ship arrest.<br>
                    <em>Mencakup: Compliance Management, Flag State & Port State Control, International Standards, Maritime Legal Framework</em>
                </li>

                <!-- Modul 6: Docking -->
                <li>
                    <strong>🔧 Docking, UWILD & Emergency Repairs</strong>
                    Drydocking fundamentals & procedures, hull inspection & steel renewal, underwater hull cleaning & coating, propeller & tailshaft overhaul, UWILD (Under Water Inspection in Lieu of Drydocking).<br>
                    <em>Mencakup: Dry Dock Planning, Underwater Inspection, Class Society Coordination, Emergency Docking Scenarios, Ship Repair Management</em>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </section>
        
